OL,3,CMusical adaptation of Pride to make
OL,4,Cworld premiere on London stage this
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FA musical production of Pride, adapted
OL,8,Ffrom the award-winning film, will make
OL,9,Fits world premiere on the London stage
OL,10,Fthis summer, it has been announced.
OL,12,FThe hit 2014 film, starring Bill Nighy
OL,13,Fand Andrew Scott, is based on the true
OL,14,Fstory of the Lesbians and Gays Support
OL,15,Fthe Miners (LGSM) campaign during the
OL,16,Flengthy strike of the National Union
OL,17,Fof Mineworkers in the 1980s.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
