PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1778505069
OL,3,CMusical adaptation of Pride to make
OL,4,Cworld premiere on London stage this
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FDirector Matthew Warchus and writer
OL,8,FStephen Beresford, who worked on the
OL,9,Foriginal film, have reunited more than
OL,10,Fa decade later to develop the upcoming
OL,11,Fmusical, which will be staged at the
OL,12,FDorfman Theatre in London this summer.
OL,14,FThe National Theatre production stars
OL,15,FJhon Lumsden and Samuel Barnett as
OL,16,Fmembers of the unlikely alliance with
OL,17,Fthe miners of South Wales ` inspired
OL,18,Fby real activists who were part of the
OL,19,FLGSM.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
