FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1778505069
OL,3,CMusical adaptation of Pride to make
OL,4,Cworld premiere on London stage this
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FIn an exclusive preview for the show,
OL,8,FMatthew Woodyatt can be seen as
OL,9,Fstriking miner Dai Donovan leading the
OL,10,Fensemble as they sing one of the songs
OL,11,Ffrom the musical, titled You Stood By
OL,12,FMe.
OL,14,FDirector Warchus said: "One of the
OL,15,Fthings about this story is that it's
OL,16,Fso unlikely to be true. You can't
OL,17,Fquite believe it."
OL,26,@vD@XOUyD@RO]
