PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1778505069
OL,3,CMusical adaptation of Pride to make
OL,4,Cworld premiere on London stage this
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FThe sneak peek also shows the cast and
OL,8,Fproduction crew gathered at the former
OL,9,Fminer's welfare hall in the Upper
OL,10,FSwansea Valley ` which was once a
OL,11,Ffocal point for the LGSM ` to meet
OL,12,Fwith members of the community who
OL,13,Finspired the film and musical.
OL,15,FReflecting on this, Beresford, who has
OL,16,Fwritten the book and lyrics for the
OL,17,Fmusical, said: "It's wonderful to be
OL,18,Fhere and hear everyone's memories of
OL,19,Fthe day when the gays invaded."
OL,26,@yD@POU{D@_O]
