PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1778505069
OL,3,CMusical adaptation of Pride to make
OL,4,Cworld premiere on London stage this
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FFollowing a sold-out preview run at
OL,8,FCardiff's Sherman Theatre, the
OL,9,Fproduction will make its debut on the
OL,10,FLondon stage in June.
OL,12,FThe musical is set to an original
OL,13,Fscore with songs inspired by protest
OL,14,Fanthems, pop, rock, disco and the
OL,15,FWelsh choral tradition, composed by
OL,16,FChristopher Nightingale, John Cohen
OL,17,Fand DJ Walde.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
