CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1778505069
OL,3,CMusical adaptation of Pride to make
OL,4,Cworld premiere on London stage this
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FThe play has been described as "funny,
OL,8,Ffierce and filled with joy", and will
OL,9,Frun at the Dorfman Theatre in London
OL,10,Ffrom June 11 to September 12 with
OL,11,Ftickets available at
OL,12,Fnationaltheatre.org.uk.
